message.content:
Neural Networks, Optimal Experiment Design, Theory. 

Neural Networks: The paper focuses on the query/action selection of a neural network learner. 

Optimal Experiment Design: The paper applies techniques from Optimal Experiment Design (OED) to guide the query/action selection of a neural network learner. 

Theory: The paper builds on the theoretical results of Fedorov [1972] and MacKay [1992] and concludes that OED-based query/action has much to offer.
